{'text': 'We live in the age of social media. Social media allows us to connect with anyone, anywhere, anytime. It allows us to discuss anything in a matter-of-fact manner.'}

{'text': '\xa0In the long run, it will be good for society if we legalize drugs. But, it will take a lot more effort than this to make this happen.'}

{'text': 'The United States is one of the only industrialized nations in the world that does not have a single facility where people can obtain medical marijuana, even though the state of California legalized medical marijuana back in 1996.'}
